reviews.text:
a good night at a good restaurant! i came with friends that can speak canto so be prepared because after ordering they will ask what kind of soup (white or red), what kind of sauce on steak (black pepper or brown), and what kind of drink you want. i also didnt see an english menu either 

quantity served is filling and the taste did not disappoint! they also give bread with butter as starter and a cold mochi candy with your drink!!
Traditional Hong Kong style steak house. Marinated steak on sizzling plate. Reasonable price. Good choice for meat lover.
Steaks are very good in here,soup also good.

vintage restaurant with affordable price
I tried the baked pork chop rice which is in good value
Food is awesome but this place has been around for a long time, the decor and condition show it. Do not feel like touching anything in the restaurant.

result.name: 哥登堡餐廳

reviews.text: 環境👌🏻 服務👌🏻
老式街坊扒房， 以前住呢區已經係我嘅飯堂， 相隔七八年再嚟水準依然， 最正扒餐及乾炒牛河肉絲炒麵
午餐至5pm都可以$45有極好飲的羅宋湯+黑椒牛扒飯連飲品。有禮貌的多位中年伙記，舒適的舊裝修加上好味道而超值的食物可以給它五星以上的評價。
經濟實惠的西餐廳，食物質素中上啦！
除了那份懷緬的心情，無再去的理由。
